description: Recorded live from Naarm/Melbourne, Great Southern Lands is an excursion through the deep Australian and New Zealand underground. Expect post-VU freakouts, dolewave jangles, forgotten lathe-cuts and avant-garde chin scratchers, served up by a bunch of Antipodean amateurs
